description:
If your opponent Ritual, Fusion, Synchro, Xyz, or Link Summons a monster(s): You can activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each effect of this card’s name once per turn);
● Add 1 “Fallen of Albaz”, or 1 monster that mentions it, from your Deck to your hand.
● Special Summon 1 “Fallen of Albaz”, or 1 monster that mentions it, from your hand.
